Execute-notify

A utility to execute a command and notify the user upon
completion. This uses libnotify.

Instructions
------------

1. Make sure the 'en' script is on your path

2. Make sure the hard-coded references to various filesystem locations are valid for your system (if not, modify properly):
   a. /bin/bash
   b. /usr/share/icons/gnome/.....

3. Make sure the 'notify-send' command is on your path

4. Enjoy.

For more information, see:
http://www.criticalexponent.org/blog/2009/12/13/execute-notify/